skins.shipDescription: Fletcher-class destroyer - Charles Ausburne, Hull Number DD-570!
skins.selfIntroduction: I'm Charles Ausburne of the Fletcher-class, and the world famous Captain of the Little Beavers! I showed my true colors at the Cape of St. George. Want to be my partner in justice, Commander?
skins.acquisition: Nice to meet you, Commander! I'm Charles Ausburne, Captain of the Little Beavers. Whoever picks on the hopeless and defenseless will receive their punishment in due time!
skins.login: Good day, Commander. Charles Ausburne, Captain of the Little Beavers, reporting in! Are there any naughty kids who need to be disciplined today?
skins.details: Weapons and gear are the iron fists of justice!
skins.secretaryIdle1: Become a friend of justice with me!
skins.secretaryIdle3: My sonar shows... it looks like your heart is beating extra fast, Commander!
skins.secretaryTouch: Mmm, I feel the justice coming from you!
